uk.ac.manchester.cs.owl.owlapi

Class MapPointer<K,V extends OWLAxiom>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.owl.owlapi.MapPointer<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - key
    V - value
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClassAxiomByClassPointer

    public class MapPointer<K,V extends OWLAxiom>
extends Object
    * Objects that identify contained maps - so that getting the keys of a specific map does not require a specific method for each map nor does it require the map to be copied and returned.
    Author:
    ignazio
